[{"id":"VR736679","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a spherical balloon in two stages in a pool. Initially, the balloon is slightly submerged just below the surface of the water and has a radius of 3 r and the buoyant force on the balloon is F sub B comma 1. The second stage shows the balloon submerged near the bottom of the pool and it now has a radius of 2 r and the buoyant force on the balloon is F sub B comma 2.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR736679.g02.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">An inflated spherical balloon is fully submerged just below the surface of a pool. The radius of the balloon is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3 lowercase r\"><math alttext=\"3 lowercase r\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>3</mn><mi>r</mi></math></span></span> and the buoyant force on the balloon is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"F sub B comma 1, end sub\"><math alttext=\"F sub B comma 1, end sub\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>F</mi><mtext>B,1</mtext></msub></math></span></span>. The balloon is then pushed further beneath the surface to a point where the water pressure has caused the radius of the balloon to be reduced to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 lowercase r\"><math alttext=\"2 lowercase r\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><mi>r</mi></math></span></span> and the buoyant force on the balloon is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"F sub B comma 2, end sub\"><math alttext=\"F sub B comma 2, end sub\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>F</mi><mtext>B,2</mtext></msub></math></span></span>. What is the ratio <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"F sub B comma 1, end sub, to F sub B comma 2, end sub\"><math alttext=\"F sub B comma 1, end sub, to F sub B comma 2, end sub\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>F</mi><mtext>B,1</mtext></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>F</mi><mtext>B,2</mtext></msub></math></span></span> ?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR736679_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1 to 1\"><math alttext=\"1 to 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3 to 2\"><math alttext=\"3 to 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>3</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>2</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"9 to 4\"><math alttext=\"9 to 4\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>9</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>4</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"27 to 8\"><math alttext=\"27 to 8\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>27</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>8</mn></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":3}]